lead_paragraph: Manchester City defender Pablo Zabaleta suspects there will be changes when new manager Pep Guardiola arrives during the close season but said the players are completely focussed on challenging for titles in the current campaign.

headline.print_headline: City Suspect Changes Upon Guardiola Arrival, Says Zabaleta
